# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/), (kinda based on this? Too lazy to do a lot of work for a change log that no one will ever read...)
and this project adheres to [Live TV Viewer](https://gitlab.com/ScaredDonut/live-tv-viewer).

## [2.3] - 2020 - 01 - 14
###Added
- Reorganized the code a bit
- Added a system that wont let you go below page 1 by using the back button. [Still working on a fix that wont let you go past max page]

## [2.2] - 2020 - 01 - 14
### Added
- Pagination will now highlight on the current page that you're on
- Work started on fixing the bug where it lets you go past max pages and below page 1.

## [2.1] - 2020 - 01 - 13
### Added
- Pagination
- maxPerPage in config is now functional

## [2.0] - 2020 - 01 - 13
### Added
- New template thanks to [BlackrockDigital](https://github.com/BlackrockDigital/) - For their [template](https://github.com/BlackrockDigital/startbootstrap-heroic-features) saved me a lot of time!
- Reorganized the format of the file
- Add comments for some stuff...
- added a simple config file so some data can be changed.
### Fixed
- Stuff will actually show up in colums rather than one long ass row


## [1.0] - 2017 - 02 - 09
### Added
- Loading XML data from SteamLive and displaying it in a simple index.php file